<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَبِالزُّبُرِ}</span> ... الكُتُبِ المَجْمُوعِ فِيهَا كَثِيرٌ مِنَ الأَحْكَامِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَكِيرِ}</span> ... إِنْكَارِي عَلَيْهِمْ، وَعُقُوبَتِي لَهُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جُدَدٌ}</span> ... ذَاتُ طَرَائِقَ وَخُطُوطٍ مُخْتَلِفَةِ الأَلْوَانِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
